WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 36=

02:27.510 --> 02:29.900
So you were prepared all along.

02:47.230 --> 02:48.070
He Simu!

02:48.620 --> 02:49.460
He Simu!

02:52.140 --> 02:52.980
He Simu,

02:53.140 --> 02:54.420
you and your father enslaved us

02:54.420 --> 02:55.580
with the Decrees all along.

02:55.990 --> 02:57.230
Now, you don't have the Lantern.

02:57.550 --> 02:59.020
How can you still restrain us?

02:59.020 --> 02:59.950
Without the Lantern,

02:59.950 --> 03:01.700
you're not the Sovereign of Spirits.

03:02.110 --> 03:02.950
Then the throne

03:03.270 --> 03:04.350
is available to anyone.

03:09.110 --> 03:10.460
It's not a throne

03:11.860 --> 03:13.300
unless I sit on it.

03:13.990 --> 03:15.270
With or without the Lantern,

03:16.830 --> 03:18.620
I am the Sovereign of Spirits.

03:45.110 --> 03:46.510
But without the Lantern,

03:47.670 --> 03:49.790
the Void will never be at peace.

03:53.550 --> 03:54.390
Simu,

03:55.670 --> 03:57.230
did you really give it to Yan Ke?

03:58.830 --> 04:00.140
Without the Lantern,

04:00.140 --> 04:01.070
you and I are peers.

04:01.900 --> 04:02.740
Come on.

04:02.740 --> 04:03.580
Let me sit on it.

04:08.580 --> 04:09.420
That explains it.

04:09.860 --> 04:11.020
Yan Ke issued an edict

04:11.020 --> 04:12.020
to the 24 Temples,

04:12.550 --> 04:14.510
calling for surrender
in the name of the Lantern.

04:15.020 --> 04:16.230
He even sent puppet spirits

04:16.230 --> 04:17.260
to attack Fusang Tree

04:17.260 --> 04:18.300
and mess up the Void.

04:18.620 --> 04:20.110
Luckily, you set up a formation

04:20.110 --> 04:21.670
to seal the exit of Fusang Tree.

04:22.230 --> 04:23.740
My father left this formation.

04:24.620 --> 04:26.300
It was meant to stop the spirits

04:26.300 --> 04:28.110
who didn't want to obey the Decrees.

04:28.620 --> 04:29.910
It's controlled by spirit power.

04:32.110 --> 04:32.990
From this day on,

04:34.260 --> 04:35.820
I'll take command of the Void.

04:36.820 --> 04:37.860
Apart from me,

04:38.470 --> 04:40.420
spirits may enter but never leave.

04:59.500 --> 05:02.180
I have such great power.

05:10.860 --> 05:12.030
Why can't I make you

05:12.030 --> 05:13.300
accept me as your master yet?

05:16.500 --> 05:18.060
Yan Ke cornered the Sovereign like this.

05:18.140 --> 05:18.990
He is

05:18.990 --> 05:20.180
also a tough one.

05:20.710 --> 05:21.990
I sent lords of Shaoling Temple

05:21.990 --> 05:22.990
and Zhuangling Temple

05:22.990 --> 05:24.230
to detain puppet spirits.

05:24.550 --> 05:26.350
But too many puppet spirits

05:26.350 --> 05:27.590
are hiding throughout the Void.

05:27.820 --> 05:29.550
It will take some days to find them all.

05:29.820 --> 05:31.030
Before, Yan Zhang

05:31.030 --> 05:33.230
could only control puppets in the Void

05:33.230 --> 05:34.740
with Chiling Secret Technique.

05:34.940 --> 05:35.860
Why can Yan Ke

05:35.860 --> 05:37.030
control those puppet spirits

05:37.030 --> 05:38.060
even in the Mortal World?

05:38.550 --> 05:39.620
He must have

05:39.910 --> 05:41.150
much stronger power now.

05:41.740 --> 05:42.710
Within such a short time,

05:42.990 --> 05:44.350
he must have devoured many spirits.

05:44.820 --> 05:46.350
He stole my Chiling Secret Technique.

05:47.500 --> 05:48.340
Thief.

05:48.620 --> 05:49.460
In that case,

05:49.990 --> 05:51.150
he even has the Lantern.

05:51.710 --> 05:53.500
Why is he trying hard

05:54.030 --> 05:55.180
to mess up the Void

05:55.180 --> 05:56.380
instead of attacking it?

05:57.030 --> 05:58.300
He does have the Lantern.

05:58.590 --> 05:59.910
But it doesn't mean he can use it.

06:00.420 --> 06:02.060
Yan Ke is making such a big scene

06:02.820 --> 06:04.380
just to pin me down

06:04.740 --> 06:05.940
and figure out how to use it.

06:06.300 --> 06:07.620
The Lantern follows the strongest.

06:07.940 --> 06:09.420
We don't know how Yan Ke

06:09.420 --> 06:10.910
has been growing his power out there.

06:11.500 --> 06:13.180
But the submission of the Lantern

06:14.420 --> 06:15.590
is only a matter of time.

06:19.740 --> 06:21.110
The Lantern

06:22.420 --> 06:23.420
won't yield to him

06:24.150 --> 06:25.740
unless I'm dead.

06:28.860 --> 06:29.700
Xu,

06:30.230 --> 06:31.620
you just recovered from the poison.

06:32.300 --> 06:33.420
Go get some more rest.

06:34.940 --> 06:36.030
I feel much better now.

06:36.820 --> 06:38.260
Luda's poison is fierce.

06:38.910 --> 06:40.260
But the physician cured me in time.

06:41.990 --> 06:42.830
Yeah.

06:49.740 --> 06:50.590
Xu,

06:50.590 --> 06:51.790
don't push yourself too hard.

06:52.110 --> 06:53.550
When Xiaoxiao calms down and returns,

06:53.790 --> 06:54.990
we'll drink and eat meat pies.

06:59.990 --> 07:00.830
You're right.

07:02.380 --> 07:03.470
She may refuse to see me.

07:04.350 --> 07:05.500
But she'll come to see you.

07:12.550 --> 07:13.390
Prophet.

07:14.620 --> 07:15.470
You're back already?

07:22.260 --> 07:23.100
These red spots...

07:23.590 --> 07:24.620
Did you meet evil spirits?

07:25.380 --> 07:27.420
It's the duty of our sect

07:27.420 --> 07:28.620
to punish the evil spirits

07:28.620 --> 07:29.460
in the Mortal World.

07:30.180 --> 07:31.020
It's just...

07:33.820 --> 07:35.470
I haven't found the elixir for you.

07:38.350 --> 07:39.710
I thought it was something serious.

07:40.500 --> 07:41.340
Never mind.

07:42.470 --> 07:43.310
Ziji.

07:47.350 --> 07:49.110
This is the Rescue Pill of our sect.

07:49.620 --> 07:51.350
It can help you restore your vitality.

07:52.110 --> 07:52.990
But it can't cure

07:52.990 --> 07:54.590
the trauma from your fading senses.

07:55.380 --> 07:56.620
That's actually irreversible.

08:10.150 --> 08:11.150
This is good enough.

08:12.380 --> 08:13.220
I'll always remember

08:13.710 --> 08:15.180
how you've saved my life.

08:18.110 --> 08:18.950
Prophet,

08:19.670 --> 08:20.710
may I ask one more favor?

08:22.110 --> 08:22.950
What is it?

08:30.590 --> 08:31.430
Could you please

08:32.430 --> 08:33.660
take a message to Simu?

08:34.260 --> 08:35.430
Tell her I'm confused

08:35.860 --> 08:37.020
and I want to see her again.

08:40.190 --> 08:41.950
I can be bold enough

08:41.950 --> 08:42.860
to take this message.

08:43.350 --> 08:44.190
But...

08:44.660 --> 08:46.380
Great Ancestor won't agree.

08:47.100 --> 08:47.950
She is

08:47.950 --> 08:49.590
quite resolute.

08:49.860 --> 08:50.830
Actually,

08:52.310 --> 08:53.190
she has always been

08:53.190 --> 08:54.350
indulgent with you.

08:55.070 --> 08:55.910
Maybe...

08:56.310 --> 08:57.540
When the war is over,

08:57.950 --> 08:59.230
you can go find her in the Void.

09:05.710 --> 09:06.660
When the war is over...

09:14.950 --> 09:16.070
Whenever she wants to see me,

09:19.020 --> 09:20.110
she can come anytime.

09:24.430 --> 09:25.270
I can't do the same.

09:30.190 --> 09:31.430
This is so unfair.

09:44.260 --> 09:45.710
You should have known it early.

09:52.740 --> 09:53.580
I know.

09:55.350 --> 09:56.590
Great Ancestor.

10:01.190 --> 10:02.190
Things are tricky?

10:03.260 --> 10:05.470
Many evil spirits
have appeared in Youzhou

10:05.470 --> 10:06.430
like attending a market.

10:06.430 --> 10:07.900
They came from other cities.

10:08.660 --> 10:10.190
It took a great deal of effort.

10:11.310 --> 10:12.150
It's Yan Ke.

10:14.140 --> 10:15.780
He took the Spirits Lantern

10:15.780 --> 10:16.780
and hid it in Youzhou.

10:17.500 --> 10:18.620
He can't operate it.

10:18.900 --> 10:20.540
But he might use it

10:21.140 --> 10:22.500
to suppress the spirits there

10:22.500 --> 10:23.380
to serve his needs.

10:23.950 --> 10:24.990
I've locked down the Void,

10:24.990 --> 10:26.110
so spirits can't get out.

10:26.780 --> 10:27.620
In the Mortal World,

10:27.990 --> 10:28.860
you must be careful.

10:29.500 --> 10:30.540
Great Ancestor,

10:31.020 --> 10:32.430
that's too much for you.

10:33.740 --> 10:35.350
You have to defend the Void

10:35.540 --> 10:36.950
and protect the Mortal World.

10:36.950 --> 10:37.790
I...

10:38.230 --> 10:39.070
Wait, wait.

10:40.740 --> 10:41.580
Great Ancestor,

10:43.260 --> 10:44.470
will you really

10:45.780 --> 10:47.430
not see him again?

10:50.310 --> 10:52.540
He asked me to take a message.

10:52.740 --> 10:53.580
He said

10:55.540 --> 10:56.900
he was confused

10:57.430 --> 10:58.830
and wanted to see you again.

11:00.740 --> 11:02.430
I'm just doing

11:02.620 --> 11:03.830
what I promised him.

11:07.310 --> 11:08.150
Are you done?

11:08.900 --> 11:10.310
The last time I saw him,

11:11.110 --> 11:12.190
he wasn't feeling very well.

11:13.710 --> 11:15.020
You just found out?

11:16.660 --> 11:17.500
Just as I thought,

11:17.500 --> 11:19.620
nothing can escape you.

11:20.430 --> 11:21.860
I didn't dare to tell you

11:22.230 --> 11:23.710
about his fading senses.

11:24.780 --> 11:25.950
I thought

11:26.310 --> 11:27.950
I could find a way to cure him.

11:28.780 --> 11:30.740
But I just can't.

11:32.710 --> 11:33.620
Great Ancestor,

11:34.590 --> 11:35.430
so...

11:37.540 --> 11:40.230
Will you go see him?

11:44.660 --> 11:46.140
Watch over Duan Shunxi.

12:20.110 --> 12:20.950
Ziji,

12:22.070 --> 12:22.910
I almost feel like

12:24.830 --> 12:26.590
I'm seeing my own ancestors.

12:28.430 --> 12:29.900
I guess I'm dying.

12:33.190 --> 12:34.030
Just a hallucination.

12:34.950 --> 12:36.020
You saw them last year.

12:40.020 --> 12:40.900
Take your medicine.

12:40.900 --> 12:41.740
Ziji,

12:43.500 --> 12:44.380
in this world,

12:45.110 --> 12:46.540
Great Ancestor must have been

12:46.540 --> 12:47.540
the best Sovereign ever.

12:51.260 --> 12:52.100
Don't you think so?

12:57.830 --> 12:59.380
The Sovereign who has no wishes

12:59.900 --> 13:02.260
restrains the spirits
born of obsessions.

13:02.950 --> 13:04.260
Everything in this world

13:05.140 --> 13:06.350
is deliberately designed

13:08.020 --> 13:09.070
with connected links

13:09.710 --> 13:10.780
just for smooth operation.

13:12.110 --> 13:12.950
Ziji.

13:14.780 --> 13:16.260
Do you think this is good?

13:18.230 --> 13:19.070
Like you said,

13:20.110 --> 13:21.560
the world operates smoothly.

13:25.140 --> 13:25.980
So,

13:27.190 --> 13:28.310
either it's Great Ancestor

13:28.310 --> 13:29.740
who doesn't want to be the Sovereign,

13:30.350 --> 13:31.590
or it's me who has a short life.

13:33.190 --> 13:34.660
Neither of us is given a choice.

13:35.140 --> 13:36.470
We're nothing but tools.

13:38.140 --> 13:39.860
Do you still think this way

13:42.950 --> 13:44.350
after living here for so long?

13:48.990 --> 13:49.830
Take your medicine.

13:50.350 --> 13:51.190
Don't change the subject.

13:55.590 --> 13:57.430
Oh no, you noticed.

13:58.020 --> 13:59.950
After I spit out

13:59.950 --> 14:00.830
that blood,

14:00.830 --> 14:01.670
I felt

14:02.140 --> 14:04.020
much more refreshed.

14:04.780 --> 14:06.830
How about

14:08.140 --> 14:09.990
I don't take this medicine?

14:35.190 --> 14:36.740
You know it doesn't work on me.

14:40.540 --> 14:41.900
You should go back soon.

15:00.470 --> 15:01.660
Youzhou has complex terrain.

15:02.020 --> 15:03.620
We managed to guard some cities.

15:04.070 --> 15:05.500
But our losses are much greater.

15:08.590 --> 15:09.430
This arrowhead

15:09.780 --> 15:10.860
is forged from Tianluo Ore

15:11.310 --> 15:12.660
just like my armor.

15:13.190 --> 15:14.350
It's lightweight and sharp

15:14.770 --> 15:15.620
and penetrates better

15:15.620 --> 15:16.470
than iron arrowheads.

15:17.590 --> 15:18.590
This is my lethal weapon

15:18.830 --> 15:19.830
for the Chong Army.

15:23.210 --> 15:24.370
Impressive.

15:24.900 --> 15:26.740
You're a genius, Marshal.

15:33.500 --> 15:34.710
Their High Priest

15:34.710 --> 15:35.900
used poison to scare us

15:35.900 --> 15:36.860
and demoralize us.

15:37.190 --> 15:38.660
Now, we have this new arrowhead.

15:39.140 --> 15:40.230
I can imagine how awesome

15:40.230 --> 15:41.990
it would be to shoot them with this.

15:45.140 --> 15:45.980
Xu.

15:48.140 --> 15:48.980
You...

15:52.110 --> 15:53.470
Go supervise the arrowhead forging

15:54.070 --> 15:54.910
and set the tactics.

15:55.990 --> 15:56.830
Yes.

15:57.860 --> 15:58.700
Let's go.

16:02.110 --> 16:02.950
Xu,

16:03.310 --> 16:04.660
Mr. Fang sent a message.

16:04.660 --> 16:05.900
He's back in Nandu for work.

16:07.580 --> 16:08.790
(Emperor of Liang fell ill.)

16:09.180 --> 16:11.630
(Prince Su and Prince Ji
besieged Nandu,)

16:11.630 --> 16:12.880
(forcing him to abdicate.)

16:13.730 --> 16:15.320
(Prince Jin and Fang Xianye)

16:15.320 --> 16:17.030
(took the Emperor to the Royal Villa.)

16:17.310 --> 16:20.110
(Without an emperor,
Nandu is in great chaos.)

16:22.100 --> 16:24.540
(Royal Villa)

16:28.660 --> 16:30.020
There you are, Fang.

16:30.660 --> 16:31.590
Your Majesty,

16:31.950 --> 16:33.830
I've brought some medicinal supplements.

16:51.260 --> 16:52.430
Over all these years,

16:53.740 --> 16:55.230
you and Duan Xu worked hard

16:56.540 --> 16:57.740
to assist my son Jin.

16:59.140 --> 17:01.310
By Your Majesty's grace,

17:01.660 --> 17:03.190
Duan Shunxi and I assist Prince Jin.

17:03.620 --> 17:04.470
It is our honor.

17:04.990 --> 17:05.870
We won't complain.

17:06.540 --> 17:08.470
The three of you are destined to meet.

17:09.390 --> 17:10.430
In the same year's exam,

17:10.780 --> 17:11.620
you were

17:11.910 --> 17:14.300
the top three scholars.

17:15.020 --> 17:17.580
And you all wanted to uphold our nation.

17:18.260 --> 17:19.910
All the officials in court

17:20.580 --> 17:21.420
either support

17:22.020 --> 17:23.150
Chancellor Du or Duke Pei.

17:24.100 --> 17:25.500
All they want to do

17:25.500 --> 17:27.100
is fight for power.

17:28.060 --> 17:29.740
They never want to help our people.

17:31.820 --> 17:33.020
I'm really relieved

17:33.990 --> 17:34.830
to see

17:35.670 --> 17:37.020
people like you.

17:39.330 --> 17:40.740
The Chong invaded our territories

17:40.820 --> 17:41.710
to enslave our people.

17:42.080 --> 17:43.430
Our people have been suffering.

17:44.020 --> 17:44.860
I became an official

17:45.150 --> 17:46.630
just to change this situation.

17:47.500 --> 17:49.100
Prince Su and Prince Ji

17:49.950 --> 17:52.430
are each backed
by Chancellor Du and Duke Pei.

17:53.020 --> 17:54.710
They want to force me to abdicate

17:55.670 --> 17:56.740
when I'm seriously ill.

17:57.950 --> 18:00.470
I won't let them have their way.

18:01.230 --> 18:02.430
I told Jin

18:03.100 --> 18:04.670
to send out secret decrees everywhere.

18:05.340 --> 18:06.180
The reinforcements

18:06.340 --> 18:08.470
will soon arrive.

18:09.780 --> 18:10.620
And of course...

18:12.300 --> 18:14.020
I also issued a decree to Duan Xu,

18:15.020 --> 18:17.020
asking him to return soon and help us.

18:25.190 --> 18:26.710
How is Miss Duan?

18:27.260 --> 18:27.910
Don't worry.

18:27.910 --> 18:28.750
Everything is fine.

18:30.100 --> 18:30.950
Send this letter

18:30.950 --> 18:31.780
to Miss Duan

18:31.780 --> 18:32.620
as fast as you can.

18:55.910 --> 18:56.990
(Decree)
Duan Xu misled the army.

18:57.390 --> 18:58.300
Duke Pei ordered

18:58.580 --> 19:00.230
all secret letters from Nandu to Youzhou

19:00.390 --> 19:01.950
should be intercepted. Let's go.

19:01.950 --> 19:02.790
Yes.

19:20.500 --> 19:21.910
What exactly is the Spirits Lantern?

19:22.740 --> 19:24.430
The supreme treasure
of the Spirit World.

19:25.260 --> 19:27.630
It can make a spirit
have immense power,

19:27.990 --> 19:29.060
command all the spirits,

19:29.580 --> 19:31.100
and reign in the Void.

19:37.190 --> 19:39.230
It's a symbol of the Sovereign

19:42.020 --> 19:44.230
and a symbol of power.

19:47.300 --> 19:48.260
The Spirits Lantern.

19:49.580 --> 19:50.870
What will happen

19:52.710 --> 19:54.150
if a human has it?

19:54.260 --> 19:59.740
(Liang)

20:12.340 --> 20:14.060
Why are evil spirits here?

21:00.870 --> 21:01.710
Yan Ke,

21:02.150 --> 21:03.260
I hear you're now a traitor

21:03.260 --> 21:04.430
that everyone wants to beat.

21:05.150 --> 21:06.430
Duan Shunxi,

21:06.990 --> 21:08.820
let's see how long you'll be laughing.

21:10.150 --> 21:10.990
(The Lantern?)

21:11.340 --> 21:12.260
(Why does he have it?)

21:26.470 --> 21:27.310
Simu,

21:28.060 --> 21:29.710
did you receive the present

21:30.020 --> 21:31.060
I left in the Void?

21:34.670 --> 21:35.630
So sad.

21:35.990 --> 21:37.100
Yan Zhang worked so hard

21:37.100 --> 21:38.430
to collect those puppets.

21:39.190 --> 21:40.150
But they were fragile.

21:41.150 --> 21:42.910
Since you don't like this present,

21:44.390 --> 21:46.630
I'll show you something else.

21:49.500 --> 21:50.540
You've shielded him

21:50.540 --> 21:51.780
so well.

21:52.150 --> 21:53.710
It took me quite a lot of trouble

21:53.710 --> 21:54.710
to take him.

21:56.430 --> 21:57.270
Simu.

22:01.870 --> 22:03.430
You know you're doomed.

22:04.670 --> 22:05.740
That's why

22:05.740 --> 22:06.870
you pull such a dirty trick.

22:07.990 --> 22:09.340
Last time, you traded the Lantern

22:09.340 --> 22:10.340
for his life.

22:11.100 --> 22:11.940
This time,

22:12.580 --> 22:14.300
what will you trade?

22:15.580 --> 22:16.500
Don't be silly.

22:19.340 --> 22:21.390
You know exactly

22:21.630 --> 22:22.870
how the Lantern works.

22:23.540 --> 22:24.710
(Simu traded the Lantern)

22:24.710 --> 22:25.550
(for my antidote.)

22:26.100 --> 22:27.870
I've done my best for him.

22:28.670 --> 22:30.340
He means nothing to me now.

22:31.500 --> 22:32.870
If you want to kill him, kill him.

22:33.910 --> 22:36.580
Simu, you're always kind to mortals.

22:36.910 --> 22:38.150
If I kill him,

22:39.740 --> 22:41.470
you'll be sad, won't you?

22:50.150 --> 22:51.820
How pathetic you are, Yan Ke.

22:54.340 --> 22:55.630
It's been 300 years.

22:56.230 --> 22:58.100
You still can't find my vital gate.

22:58.950 --> 23:00.150
I gave you the Lantern,

23:00.150 --> 23:01.190
but you can't use it.

23:01.950 --> 23:02.910
You can't beat me

23:03.100 --> 23:04.020
and you can't kill me.

23:04.540 --> 23:05.630
You've even fallen for me.

23:06.500 --> 23:08.300
Now all you can do is threaten me

23:08.300 --> 23:09.340
with a mere mortal.

23:12.470 --> 23:14.670
How could you be so silly?

23:21.060 --> 23:22.820
Seeing how miserable you are,

23:24.580 --> 23:25.910
let me tell you something.

23:27.470 --> 23:28.710
300 years ago,

23:29.740 --> 23:31.580
I tore out my vital gate

23:32.710 --> 23:34.100
and melted it into the Lantern.

23:45.740 --> 23:46.670
As for him...

23:48.260 --> 23:49.710
His business isn't my concern.

23:50.910 --> 23:52.020
You can't kill me

23:54.020 --> 23:55.740
unless you destroy the Lantern.

24:00.500 --> 24:01.910
But would you do that?

24:05.500 --> 24:06.710
You traded the Lantern for me.

24:07.470 --> 24:08.630
So you care about me!

24:21.500 --> 24:24.100
Only a real rival makes it exciting.

24:26.060 --> 24:27.340
You're right, Simu.

24:29.060 --> 24:30.540
I wouldn't destroy it.

25:14.710 --> 25:16.060
I told you.

25:17.150 --> 25:19.020
She's never had trouble finding love.

25:20.430 --> 25:21.740
What do you think you are?

25:23.060 --> 25:24.910
You're just nothing.

25:26.150 --> 25:27.910
She traded the Lantern for you

25:28.260 --> 25:30.390
because she had a backup plan.

25:35.430 --> 25:37.670
If she really had to lose something,

25:38.020 --> 25:39.670
she wouldn't hesitate to leave you.

25:40.740 --> 25:42.340
She fooled you.

25:43.300 --> 25:44.780
You're just a toy.

25:45.870 --> 25:46.870
I don't believe it.

25:48.540 --> 25:50.230
Simu wouldn't do this to me.

25:51.800 --> 25:52.670
I used to think

25:52.670 --> 25:54.020
the physician cured me.

25:55.260 --> 25:56.190
I just found out

25:57.260 --> 25:58.190
Simu traded the Lantern

25:58.190 --> 25:59.030
for my life.

26:00.020 --> 26:01.300
She wouldn't give up on me.

26:01.820 --> 26:02.670
Stop daydreaming!

26:05.300 --> 26:07.230
Since He Simu has abandoned you,

26:07.570 --> 26:08.430
you're no longer

26:08.430 --> 26:09.670
of any use to me.

26:15.060 --> 26:16.430
Even if she doesn't care about me,

26:18.100 --> 26:19.060
she has to care

26:19.060 --> 26:20.190
about her spell bearer.

26:21.540 --> 26:22.820
She wouldn't leave me alone.

26:38.340 --> 26:40.430
Since you're her spell bearer,

26:43.100 --> 26:44.060
you can

26:44.060 --> 26:45.950
exchange senses anytime.

26:48.390 --> 26:50.580
I want you to exchange senses with her

26:50.580 --> 26:52.060
at the moment I tell you.

26:52.580 --> 26:54.740
When I defeat and capture her,

26:55.580 --> 26:57.710
the Lantern will take me as its master.

26:58.630 --> 27:00.820
Then I'll make her stay by your side

27:01.630 --> 27:02.910
for the rest of your life.

27:03.870 --> 27:04.710
What do you say?

27:09.390 --> 27:10.340
Where's Marshal Duan?

27:10.340 --> 27:11.190
Why is he gone?

27:11.190 --> 27:12.390
Still no news of Marshal Duan?

27:15.150 --> 27:16.500
Terrible enemies.

27:16.950 --> 27:18.300
They want to annihilate us

27:18.300 --> 27:19.740
when Marshal Duan isn't here.

27:20.020 --> 27:21.150
We can't let them win!

27:21.910 --> 27:22.780
Commandant Xia,

27:22.780 --> 27:23.670
you lead reinforcements

27:23.670 --> 27:24.710
to Fengzhou right now.

27:24.910 --> 27:25.990
Rest assured. Count on me.

27:26.150 --> 27:26.990
Meng Wan,

27:26.990 --> 27:28.470
Qizhou is our granary.

27:28.670 --> 27:30.020
You must guard it well!

27:30.020 --> 27:30.910
Yes!

27:30.910 --> 27:31.750
Report!

27:32.670 --> 27:34.430
The Chong army is attacking fiercely!

27:35.000 --> 27:35.870
Now?

27:35.870 --> 27:37.190
- Yeah.
- What do we do?

27:39.190 --> 27:40.300
I'll serve as the vanguard.

27:40.860 --> 27:41.710
Youzhou determines

27:41.710 --> 27:42.740
the fate of the war

27:43.020 --> 27:44.670
and hundreds of thousands of lives.

27:45.100 --> 27:46.100
Xu isn't here now.

27:46.260 --> 27:47.260
We must fight desperately

27:47.540 --> 27:48.380
and never retreat.

27:57.260 --> 27:58.430
Protect yourself.

28:08.740 --> 28:10.100
The puppet spirits caught yesterday

28:10.340 --> 28:12.060
have all been put in the Prison.

28:12.340 --> 28:13.500
The unrest in the Void

28:13.710 --> 28:14.780
has been quelled for now.

28:15.470 --> 28:17.150
Yan Ke is right there in Youzhou.

28:17.870 --> 28:19.710
I'll take him down myself.

28:20.430 --> 28:21.580
I have my own plans

28:22.470 --> 28:23.870
for the Mortal World.

28:51.870 --> 28:53.260
Xiaoxiao.

28:58.390 --> 28:59.710
Xiaoxiao.

30:41.870 --> 30:42.710
Xiaoxiao!

30:44.020 --> 30:44.990
Xiaoxiao.

30:45.780 --> 30:46.620
Xiaoxiao.

30:48.060 --> 30:48.990
Xiaoxiao!

30:49.630 --> 30:51.020
I just want to follow you.

30:51.020 --> 30:53.150
I can eat less.

30:55.100 --> 30:56.100
You took care of me.

30:56.300 --> 30:57.190
Now I have money.

30:57.190 --> 30:58.030
I'll take care of you.

30:59.230 --> 31:00.910
Xiaoxiao is a nice person.

31:01.540 --> 31:03.230
She would never make me kill anyone!

31:12.230 --> 31:15.480
♪Cross your legs♪

31:15.480 --> 31:18.340
(Liang)

31:20.080 --> 31:27.790
♪Subdue dragon and tiger;
tether horse and ape♪

31:28.160 --> 31:35.250
♪Mind still as water,
breath soft as silk♪

31:35.630 --> 31:43.070
♪Be a sage, not an immortal♪

31:44.260 --> 31:51.470
♪Cross your legs for three years♪

31:52.180 --> 31:59.560
♪Subdue dragon and tiger;
tether horse and ape♪

32:00.330 --> 32:06.950
♪Mind still as water,
breath soft as silk♪

32:07.310 --> 32:15.060
♪Be a sage, not an immortal♪

32:16.320 --> 32:23.450
♪A lamp in the east lights the west♪

32:24.350 --> 32:31.410
♪No lamp in the west,
but it's still bright♪

32:31.740 --> 32:33.670
Xiaoxiao, don't die.

32:35.230 --> 32:37.340
I promise I'll grow stronger.

32:38.470 --> 32:39.630
The General said

32:39.870 --> 32:41.630
those who always protect others

32:41.910 --> 32:43.260
are very lonely.

32:44.420 --> 32:45.260
From now on,

32:45.260 --> 32:46.470
the General and I

32:46.470 --> 32:47.870
will protect you together

32:48.430 --> 32:50.300
just like how you protected us.

32:51.060 --> 32:51.910
All right?

32:54.900 --> 33:00.460
(Liang)

33:13.540 --> 33:22.860
(Tomb of My Brother Xue Chenying)

33:40.390 --> 33:41.710
So Xiaoxiao,

33:41.710 --> 33:42.910
you're a magician.

33:47.300 --> 33:49.820
(Tomb of My Brother Xue Chenying)

34:20.580 --> 34:26.260
(Tomb of My Brother Xue Chenying)

34:41.350 --> 34:42.220
Simu,

34:42.220 --> 34:43.430
it's been a long time.

34:44.470 --> 34:46.580
You finally dared to come
out of the Glazed Pagoda.

34:47.790 --> 34:49.020
Try to trap me

34:49.580 --> 34:50.910
in this little formation?

34:52.020 --> 34:53.950
This is especially for you.

34:54.660 --> 34:56.270
It's not perfect yet.

34:56.500 --> 34:58.620
But trapping you for a little while

34:59.180 --> 35:00.020
will suffice.

35:09.620 --> 35:10.500
Now.

35:11.500 --> 35:12.580
It is time.

35:37.390 --> 35:38.270
The formation blocks

35:38.270 --> 35:39.270
He Simu's aura.

35:40.870 --> 35:42.310
The blessed flower won't work.

35:44.390 --> 35:45.870
What are you plotting?

35:48.830 --> 35:50.310
Her vital gate is in the Lantern.

35:51.950 --> 35:53.350
Maybe we can use that

35:54.140 --> 35:55.020
to exchange senses.

36:06.580 --> 36:07.660
I need a blessed flower

36:07.660 --> 36:08.500
to exchange senses.

36:10.500 --> 36:11.790
This is the last one.

36:12.990 --> 36:13.950
After it activates,

36:14.470 --> 36:15.910
the spell must be done

36:15.910 --> 36:16.750
within a short while.

36:17.220 --> 36:18.310
Or it will be useless.

36:18.620 --> 36:19.460
Duan Xu,

36:19.700 --> 36:20.540
don't be stupid.

36:23.220 --> 36:24.350
Are you scared, Your Grace?

36:25.100 --> 36:26.580
When you gave up on me,

36:27.470 --> 36:28.910
did you see this coming?

36:58.100 --> 36:58.950
You ant!

36:59.470 --> 37:00.660
How dare you grab the Lantern?

37:17.700 --> 37:18.910
A human can also

37:18.910 --> 37:19.910
use the Spirits Lantern.

37:20.310 --> 37:21.350
Yan Ke,

37:22.500 --> 37:23.660
I have to thank you

37:23.660 --> 37:25.790
for the spirit power you gave me.

37:54.750 --> 37:55.590
Duan Xu.

38:05.020 --> 38:05.860
Simu.

38:08.470 --> 38:09.310
Sorry.

38:10.620 --> 38:11.470
I failed to help you

38:11.470 --> 38:12.790
get back the Lantern.

38:55.020 --> 38:55.860
Great Ancestor.

39:00.990 --> 39:02.060
I'll leave you alone.

39:12.750 --> 39:13.910
You spat blood

39:16.830 --> 39:18.390
because of the sense exchange,

39:20.540 --> 39:21.380
didn't you?

39:25.750 --> 39:27.470
Why did you keep it from me?

39:29.870 --> 39:30.870
If I had told you,

39:36.700 --> 39:37.750
you wouldn't

39:37.750 --> 39:38.790
exchange senses anymore.

39:43.470 --> 39:45.390
Then you couldn't feel the colors,

39:47.220 --> 39:48.060
warmth,

39:50.140 --> 39:50.980
scent,

39:52.830 --> 39:53.670
or melody.

39:57.700 --> 39:58.540
Too bad, then.

40:03.220 --> 40:04.100
Duan Shunxi.

40:04.260 --> 40:07.300
♪Falling down like snow♪

40:07.310 --> 40:08.990
What am I in your eyes?

40:12.350 --> 40:13.500
A bad woman who will

40:14.220 --> 40:15.910
drain your senses and then walk off?

40:18.020 --> 40:19.470
Won't I feel sad?

40:20.500 --> 40:21.790
Don't I have a heart?

40:24.620 --> 40:25.540
I know

40:25.540 --> 40:26.830
you wouldn't drain my senses.

40:27.830 --> 40:28.870
I willingly lent you

40:28.870 --> 40:29.830
all my senses.

40:31.950 --> 40:32.990
And I've never expected

40:32.990 --> 40:34.020
to live a very long life.

40:36.270 --> 40:37.950
Compared to your lifespan...

40:38.830 --> 40:42.330
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

40:43.020 --> 40:44.180
Mine would never be long.

40:46.470 --> 40:47.540
To me,

40:49.270 --> 40:50.500
the senses are just feelings.

40:52.580 --> 40:53.830
But to you...

40:54.300 --> 40:57.700
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

40:58.580 --> 40:59.620
They mean the whole world.

41:02.040 --> 41:04.730
♪As all things turn and flow♪

41:05.140 --> 41:06.790
What do you mean "just feelings"?

41:10.910 --> 41:11.750
Duan Shunxi.

41:13.470 --> 41:15.100
You live only once.

41:15.950 --> 41:17.060
For only a few decades.

41:17.700 --> 41:19.350
Your senses are also your whole world.

41:19.790 --> 41:21.020
Can you understand?

41:21.020 --> 41:21.910
To me, you...

41:39.620 --> 41:40.460
Do you know

41:42.470 --> 41:44.020
why I left you?

41:46.910 --> 41:48.580
You didn't want Yan Ke to hurt me

41:48.750 --> 41:49.660
because of our bond.

41:52.470 --> 41:53.830
It's just one of the reasons.

41:56.390 --> 41:57.910
There's one more important reason.

42:00.470 --> 42:01.620
I've realized...

42:04.220 --> 42:05.060
I've realized

42:06.540 --> 42:08.020
I love you far too much.

42:08.020 --> 42:10.720
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

42:10.750 --> 42:12.220
I can't accept

42:13.110 --> 42:13.990
that one day

42:13.990 --> 42:14.910
I have to helplessly

42:14.910 --> 42:16.100
watch you leave me.

42:16.600 --> 42:20.460
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

42:20.690 --> 42:24.130
♪Let me wander through♪

42:24.360 --> 42:27.390
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

42:27.470 --> 42:28.580
All men die.

42:28.580 --> 42:30.800
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

42:30.830 --> 42:32.200
I think you're used to that.

42:32.200 --> 42:36.000
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

42:36.160 --> 42:38.930
♪As all things turn and flow♪

42:40.020 --> 42:40.860
Yes.

42:42.620 --> 42:43.750
I'm used to that.

42:45.270 --> 42:46.140
And I'm tired of that.

42:47.430 --> 42:48.660
I won't feel sad

42:48.660 --> 42:49.910
and I want to see no more of it.

42:50.140 --> 42:51.270
But when it comes to you,

42:52.500 --> 42:53.990
I still can't accept that.

42:59.580 --> 43:00.420
I never want

43:02.830 --> 43:04.470
to leave anyone again.

43:08.350 --> 43:09.190
Simu.

43:12.310 --> 43:13.500
Chenying died in war.

43:14.540 --> 43:16.810
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

43:16.830 --> 43:17.870
I buried him

43:17.870 --> 43:18.830
next to his father.

43:18.830 --> 43:21.920
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

43:22.070 --> 43:24.910
♪Moments may last♪

43:25.120 --> 43:33.530
♪Love and hate will fade away♪

43:38.561 --> 43:43.891
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:44.221 --> 43:48.471
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:49.831 --> 43:55.201
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:55.501 --> 44:00.101
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:01.191 --> 44:03.031
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:15.241 --> 44:20.681
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

44:20.861 --> 44:25.191
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:26.561 --> 44:31.951
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:32.181 --> 44:36.121
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:37.891 --> 44:39.781
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:42.441 --> 44:45.601
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:45.601 --> 44:48.131
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:48.131 --> 44:53.651
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:53.651 --> 44:56.891
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:56.891 --> 45:01.751
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

45:02.091 --> 45:05.111
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

45:05.111 --> 45:07.931
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

45:08.191 --> 45:10.721
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

45:10.721 --> 45:16.141
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

45:16.311 --> 45:19.381
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

45:19.541 --> 45:24.441
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

45:24.651 --> 45:28.121
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
